															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610182118" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;" >NatVoltaic</a></span> <span class="odate time_1528925997 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">13 Jun 2018 21:39</span>
