			<div class="content" id="post-content-3834832">
									

<p>Team &quot;A Weapon to Surpass Metal Gear&quot; is coming in hot and is ready to punch Nazis.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528925997" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;">OthellotheCat</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528925997" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1436137); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1436137&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528925997" alt="fieldstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1436137)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1436137); return false;">fieldstone</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528925997" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/