;timestamp=1528925997" alt="ChaoSera" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2227264)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chaosera" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2227264); return false;">ChaoSera</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528925997" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;">sirpudding</a></span> for their feedback and brainstorming help.</p>
